title: Independent candidate Abdul Latif wins NA-1
content:
ISLAMABAD, Feb 9 (APP): Independent candidate Abdul Latif won the election for National Assembly constituency NA-1 Uppar Chiral/Lower Chitral by securing 61,834 votes.
According to the unofficial result issued by the Returning Officer/ECP, his runner-up was Talha Mehmood Jamiat Ulma-e-Islam Pakistan (JUI) Candidate, who bagged 42,984 votes.
